</div>
<div class="exampleblock">
<div class="content">
<div class="paragraph">
<p><strong>Item bundles</strong></p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="paragraph">
<p>The <strong>number of returned items from item bundles</strong> will be analyzed. However, the corresponding <u>revenue will not</u>.</p>
</div>
<div class="paragraph">
<p><strong>Show details (mouseover)</strong></p>
</div>
<div class="paragraph">
<p>Point your <strong>cursor</strong> at one of the elements in the statistic in order to see <strong>details</strong> about that particular element.</p>
</div>
